
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row align-items-center min-vh-50">
        <!-- Left Side: Bigger Image -->
     <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
            <img src="~/img\about.jpeg" 
                 alt="About Project Management System" 
                 class="img-fluid rounded shadow about-image">
        </div>

        <!-- Right Side: Text -->
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h1 class="mb-4">About Our Project Management System</h1>
            <p class="lead">
                Our Project Management System (PMS) is designed to simplify the way teams plan, track, and deliver projects.
                Inspired by tools like Jira, Zoho, and GitHub Projects, PMS provides an all-in-one platform to manage tasks,
                deadlines, and team collaboration efficiently.
            </p>
            <p>
                Whether you are a startup, a growing business, or an enterprise, our system adapts to your needs, offering
                features like role-based access, task tracking, reporting, and real-time collaboration. We focus on making
                project management easy, effective, and enjoyable.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled mt-4">
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success"></i> User & Admin Dashboards</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success"></i> Task and Project Tracking</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success"></i> Real-time Collaboration</li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success"></i> Responsive & Modern Design</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Our Mission Section -->
    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col text-center">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="mt-3">
                To empower teams with an intuitive, efficient, and collaborative project management platform that ensures
                timely delivery, improved productivity, and clear communication.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Custom CSS -->
<style>>
.about-image {
    width: 100%;             /* Fill the full width of its column */
    height: auto;            /* Maintain aspect ratio */
    max-height: 500px;       /* Increase the height limit */
    object-fit: cover;       /* Make image cover space without distortion */
    border-radius: 15px;     /* Rounded corners */
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}


.about-image:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);  /* Slight zoom on hover */
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}
</style>